					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Pretty cool. Caught one error. In the first sentence of the description, &quot;apart&quot; should be &quot;a part.&quot; When used as a single word it means &quot;separate from&quot; rather than &quot;attached to.&quot; I'm going to see about doing the edit, but I figured I should mention it here first in case I screw it up somehow and accidentally blow up the whole damn thing.</p> <p>Edit: Mission accomplished. I think.</p> 
				 	]]>
